column5: June 3-23rd Got lotsa fishin plans but if there is something relatively easy access that I shouldn't miss out on let me know. PM's welcomed.
Are you still doing the river trip? If you're open to ideas I can point you in the direction of some awesome walleye lakes.
Yep doing two diff rivers but am certainly open to some Dore. Only have the canoe though not hauling my boat out there.
Up there almost any body of water will have fish!!!
Last buump before I go, packing now
